# Remark ignore patterns
# Configuration files
*.config.*
*.js
*.mjs
.remarkrc.*

# Build and output directories
**/.cache/
**/coverage/
**/dist-*/
**/dist/
**/node_modules/
**/playwright-report/
**/temp/
**/test-results/
**/tmp/
**/target/
**/vendor/
**/snapshots/


# Binary and media files
*.gif
*.ico
*.jpeg
*.jpg
*.pdf
*.png
*.wasm

# Temporary files
**/*.swp
**/*.tmp
**/*~

# Generated content
**/auto-generated/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/generated/

# API reference files (if auto-generated)
**/api-reference/

# Changelog and similar files with different formatting needs
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/HISTORY.md

# Documentation that may have different formatting requirements
**/LICENSE
docs/docusaurus/build/
docs/docusaurus/docs/
docs/docusaurus/node_modules/

# Docusaurus API reference files (if auto-generated)
**/site-docs/developer/api/
